      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in an immaculate state, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every component, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare. This is an unrivaled opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of exemplary provenance and showroom-quality condition.",
