    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible, flawless shape that it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. I'm honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been kept in truly pristine condition, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
