    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a fully overhauled VANOS system, ensuring optimal variable valve timing and internal pressure. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Every bushing, damper, and control arm is in peak operational condition, maintaining the factory-spec kinematic balance. With original paint depth and a concours-level engine bay, this example offers a visceral driving experience defined by linear throttle response and telepathic steering feedback.",
